{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<section>","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>O <strong>elemento HTML&nbsp;<code>&lt;section&gt;</code></strong>&nbsp;representa uma seção genérica&nbsp;contida em um documento HTML, geralmente com um título, quando não existir um elemento semântico mais específico para representá-lo.</p>\n\n<p>Por exemplo, um menu de navegação deve estar dentro um elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>, mas uma lista de resultados de pesquisa ou a exibição de um mapa e seus controles não possuem elementos específicos, e podem ser colocados dentro de uma &lt;section&gt;.</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\">Categorias de conteúdo</a></th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">Conteúdo de fluxo</a>&nbsp;, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#sectioning_content\">conteúdo de seção</a>, conteúdo palpável.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Conteúdo permitido</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">Conteúdo de fluxo</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Omissão de tags</th>\n   <td>Sem omissão de tags</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Tags-pai permitidas</th>\n   <td>Qualquer elemento que aceite&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">conteúdo de fluxo</a>. Note que um elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a> não deve ser um descendente de um elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Regras ARIA permitidas</th>\n   <td><code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#alert\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">alert</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#alertdialog\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">alertdialog</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#application\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">application</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#banner\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">banner</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#complementary\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">complementary</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#contentinfo\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">contentinfo</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#dialog\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">dialog</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#document\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">document</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#feed\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">feed</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#log\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">log</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#main\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">main</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#marquee\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">marquee</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#navigation\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">navigation</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#search\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">search</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#status\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">status</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#tabpanel\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">tabpanel</a></code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Interface DOM</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"Atributos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Este elemento inclui apenas os&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">atributos globais</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notas_de_uso","title":"Notas de uso","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Cada&nbsp;<code>&lt;section&gt;</code>&nbsp;deve ser identificado, geralmente incluindo um cabeçalho (elemento <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>-<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>) como um filho do elemento <code>&lt;section&gt;</code>.</li>\n <li>Se faz sentido distribuir separadamente o conteúdo de um elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>, use um elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a> em seu lugar.</li>\n <li>Não use o elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a> como um container genérico; para isso que&nbsp;a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a> serve, especialmente quando a seção é apenas&nbsp;com propósito de estilização. Uma regra de ouro é ,\"usar quando uma seção deve aparecer logicamente na estrutura de um documento\".</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo_1","title":"Exemplo 1","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"antes","title":"Antes","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Cabeçalho<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Um monte de conteúdo incrível<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"depois","title":"Depois","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Cabeçalho<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Um monte de conteúdo incrível<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo_2","title":"Exemplo 2","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"antes_2","title":"Antes","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Cabeçalho<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>passaro.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">alt</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>pássaro<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"depois_2","title":"Depois","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Cabeçalho<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>passaro.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">alt</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>pássaro<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>​​​​​\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentários</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/sections.html#the-section-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;section&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/sections.html#the-section-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;section&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/sections.html#the-section-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;section&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>5</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/4\" title=\"Released on 2011-03-22.\">4.0</a> (2.0)</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>11.10</td>\n   <td>4.1</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>2.2</td>\n   <td>4.0 (2.0)</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>11.0</td>\n   <td>5.0 (iOS 4.2)</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"<span class=\"short_text\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"pt\"><span class=\"hps\">Veja também</span></span>","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><span class=\"short_text\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"pt\">Outros elemtnos relacionados</span>: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>;</li>\n <li class=\"last\"><a class=\"deki-ns current\" href=\"/en-US/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document\" title=\"en/Sections and Outlines of an HTML5 document\">Seções e estrurura do um documento HTML5</a>.</li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"Veja também"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Atributos","id":"atributos"},{"text":"Notas de uso","id":"notas_de_uso"},{"text":"Exemplo 1","id":"exemplo_1"},{"text":"Exemplo 2","id":"exemplo_2"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"<span class=\"short_text\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"pt\"><span class=\"hps\">Veja também</span></span>","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O elemento HTML <section> representa uma seção genérica contida em um documento HTML, geralmente com um título, quando não existir um elemento semântico mais específico para representá-lo.","popularity":0.0025,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<section>: um Abschnitten zu erstellen","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<section>: The Generic Section element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"section","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<section> : l'élément de section générique","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<section>: 汎用セクション要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<section>: 일반 구획 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<section>","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"<section>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<section>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-b